{"name": "odoo-addon-product-packaging-level", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-product-packaging-level", "version": "16.0.1.2.0.6", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute", "license": "LGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo", "openupgradelib"], "summary": "This module binds a product packaging to a packaging level", "upload_time": 1731038142}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-LGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: LGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fproduct--attribute-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/product-attribute\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/16.0/product_packaging_level\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/product-attribute-16-0/product-attribute-16-0-product_packaging_level\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/product-attribute&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Product Packaging Level\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:75e11fae4004a39e651e1162643c5ec763d00d748cec9d0478e483067b24c164\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module binds a product packaging to a packaging level.\n\nThere are usually 3 levels:\n\n- The primary: it is the closest to the product, also called the retail packaging\n- The secondary: it allows to ship the products already in the primary packaging, like a box\n- The tertiary: it allows to ship large quantities in warehousing, like a pallet\n\nThis differentiates from the odoo standard package type that is typing the packaging in a more\nprecise way and that can serve for put-away routing in the warehouse.\n\nFor example a small box and a large box, or an EPAL pallet and CHEP pallet.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo create a new packaging level:\n\n1. Go to *Inventory > Configuration > Products > Product Packaging Level*.\n2. You can create/edit/delete packaging levels\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues/new?body=module:%20product_packaging_level%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Camptocamp](https://www.camptocamp.com)\n\n  - Damien Crier \\<<mailto:damien.crier@camptocamp.com>>\n  - Hiep (Nguyen Hoang) \\<<mailto:hiepnh@trobz.com>>\n  - Hoang Diep \\<<mailto:hoang@trobz.com>>\n\n- Christopher Ormaza \\<<mailto:chris.ormaza@forgeflow.com>>\n\n- Denis Roussel \\<<mailto:denis.roussel@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/product-attribute](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/16.0/product_packaging_level) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level.models.stock_package_type", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Camptocamp (<https://www.camptocamp.com>).", "License LGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl.html)"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level.models.stock_package_type.StockPackageType", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level.models.stock_package_type.StockPackageType._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level.models.stock_package_type.StockPackageType.packaging_level_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level.models.product_packaging_level", "documentation": ["Copyright 2019-2020 Camptocamp (<https://www.camptocamp.com>).", "License LGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl.html)"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level.models.product_packaging_level.ProductPackagingLevel", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addo